ygData.subject: Need a price check?

ygData.messageBody:
First of all, THANKS to the people who helped me
with my lag problem. The info you gave me worked and I
REALLY appreciate it!<br>And second, does anyone know
the price for heavy dragonhorn boots? AC17 agi+9
svm+5<br>Eqprices says they go for 12,200k and Allakhazam says
7,500 but... eh.. you know how the prices are online.
Almost never accurate. And I'm attempting to sale some
on The Erollisi Marr server and some guy offered me
1.5k for them but I say someone selling boots that
aren't as good as these (have one less stat to all) for
2.5k<br>So I am stuck =( I'm not sure what to do and I don't
want to make a mistake and sell them for too much or
too less. Any opinions would help me out a lot
=)<br><br>Zakazee Soulstealer<br>Erollisi Marr server
